<p>A preparatory peak for the World Summit on Free Information Infrastructures, a gathering of Free Infrastructure developers of all kinds between the 1st and 3rd October 2005 in London. Learn more on the <a href="http://okfn.org/wsfii/wiki/">WSFII Wiki</a>.</p>
<p>Please register here if you wish to attend WSFII. We want to be open to all but our venue has a maximum capacity. At this time, there is no registration fee, but when plans are more definite, there might be a token registration 'deposit', just so we know how many people are coming.</p>




